{"tid":1907692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返番去6月前嘅連登lu","createTime":"2020-03-02T18:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T20:22:47.000Z","uid":303858,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8d86adda8faa51936c69143e8096e52ca9d825","tid":1907692,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:51:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自high完未</span></span></strong><br />\n成個熱門全部都係on9 po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚野著咩褸反映你係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野靚女圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有好撚多炒股票嘅po<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係林奠都唔驚你班人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明大家可能好攰，好辛苦，想抖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全冇問題，可以照覆呢啲po，但係可唔可以用不推文回覆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經好撚多PR公司發功，想係連登洗走呢場運動<br />\n唔撚明點解仲有人可以推呢啲po 推返重要po啦好嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未完架 堅持咗8個月 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊繼續行落去呀</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4986b25d44684cf2d62096064a671f5865c3c609","tid":1907692,"uid":258566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T18:53:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5533c0fc7ede88fd0974e8e9ecae0c664bda2af8","tid":1907692,"uid":35456,"like":0,